# featureName

**Instance Property**

A feature name that the CoreML model defines.

## Declaration

```swift
var featureName: String? { get }
```

## Discussion

This value is [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/ObjectiveC/nil-227m0] if the observation isn’t the result of a [doc://Vision/documentation/Vision/VNCoreMLRequest] operation.

## Parsing Observation Content

- **pixelBuffer**: The image that results from a request with image output.
